    <title>Provide meter reading services to other electricity vendors</title>
    <para>
        Currently REMIG only performs meter reading in the context of selling electricity to their clients. The company is, however, considering
        to use its infrastructure to provide meter reading services to city councils and other electricity vendors.
    </para>
